  "Description": {
    "English": "A vial of the portal's <span class=\"name name-technology\">blue amber</span>, given to you by Iteration: Mercury. The ether of the Atlas itself, this is primeval liquid from which it weaves the multiverse.<br><br>A valuable and exotic component, this would be of great use to Iteration: Tethys in <span class=\"name name-technology\">repairing</span> the shattered Drone.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "迭代：墨丘利交给你的小瓶子，里面装有传送门的<span class=\"name name-technology\">蓝色琥珀</span>。作为阿特拉斯自身的以太，这种原初液体拥有着编织多元宇宙的能力。<br><br>极其珍贵的异星构件，能够帮助迭代：特提斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修复</span>破碎的无人机。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一瓶傳送門<span class=\"name name-technology\">藍琥珀</span>，是迭代：墨丘利交給你的。是寰宇自身的乙太，它用以編織多重宇宙的原始液體。<br><br>一種珍貴的奇特元件，在迭代：忒堤斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修理</span>破碎的無人機時，會十分有用。"
  },
